", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "104972450X"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q78071348", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "S", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/de/articles/006089/2011-11-25"}